  "prompt": "What are some cute names to call your boyfriend in Spanish?",
  "response": "Here are some cute names you can call your boyfriend in Spanish:\n\n1. **Cari\u00f1o** - Darling\n2. **Amor** - Love\n3. **Cielo** - Heaven or Sky\n4. **Coraz\u00f3n** - Heart\n5. **Rey** - King\n6. **G\u00fcerito** - Light-skinned or fair-haired (often used affectionately)\n7. **Princeso** - Little prince\n8. **Chiquito** - Little one or small\n9. **Osito** - Little bear\n10. **Churro** - Sweet treat (also means a type of pastry)\n11. **Papi** - Daddy (can be used affectionately)\n12. **Beb\u00e9** - Baby\n13. **Ternura** - Sweetness\n14. **Dulzura** - Sweetness\n15. **Mi Sol** - My sun\n\nFeel free to choose one that best matches your boyfriend's personality and the nature of your relationship!",
